THE GAME
--------

  'Flecho' is a Workbench game played on a square board where a
number of arrows are pointing randomly, around those arrows are
various numbers. The idea is to rotate arrows so the right amount
of arrows are pointing to each number. Complete the game in the
least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-4 different board sizes to play with.

-A game you can play while waiting for other tasks to complete...
 or just for fun!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50 kilobytes, so
 it doesn't take ages to download ...although, you can play
 another of my Workbench games while downloading this game ;)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

